  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u00a0180\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd3\u0dba \u0da2\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two Indians arrested with gold worth 180 lakhs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two Indian national airline passengers who tried to bring a stock of jewelery worth one crore eighty lakh rupees (18 million rupees) to Sri Lanka illegally were arrested by a group of officers of the Customs Narcotics Control Division at the arrival terminal of Katunayake Airport in the early hours of 08/20. .",
        "They are two businessmen, aged 28 and 38, who frequently fly between Sri Lanka and India and do business.",
        "They had arrived at Katunayake Airport on 08/20 around 02:00 AM from Chennai, India on Indigo Airlines Flight 6E1207.",
        "At the arrival terminal of Katunayake Airport, the officers of the Customs Narcotics Control Division made this arrest while they were trying to leave the airport through the undisclosed \"Green Channel\".",
        "They had taken the necklaces in the shoes and underwear they were wearing and had taken this stock of jewelery weighing 01 kg and 200 grams. The necklaces with the necklaces were plated with silver to convince the customs officials that they were not gold and to mislead them.",
        "At present, these two Indian nationals are under arrest and the airport customs officials are conducting further investigations on this matter."
      ],
